<item>
            <title>[CRYPTO-166] Library is reloaded multiple times</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CRYPTO-166</link>
                <project id="12320024" key="CRYPTO">Commons Crypto</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It looks like the JNI code keeps reloading the library, from which it then has to retrieve the symbols it needs.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This is inefficient, and it means the handle reference count is increased unnecessarily.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
